parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or become stuck in gear, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or stops moving
the transmission locks up
the vehicle jumps out of gear
the transmission sticks
the vehicle hesitates upon acceleration
the check engine light comes on
the transmission makes a whining or grinding noise
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power and acceleration, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The transmission hesitates upon acceleration
the vehicle has a delayed response when shifting
the transmission makes a whining or grinding noise
the vehicle has a sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission control module can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the transmission makes a whining or grinding noise
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the transmission hesitates upon acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The SRS light on the dashboard stays on
the airbag indicator light illuminates
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of a crash
the passenger side airbag is defective
the wiring to or within the passenger side airbag is defective.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unavailability of Replacement Parts for Airbag Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of replacement parts for the airbag recall can leave vehicles with defective airbag systems on the road, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The manufacturer advises that no replacement parts are available
the part to do the recall repair is unavailable
the dealer confirms that the part is not available.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key is difficult to remove from the ignition
the key fails to start the vehicle intermittently
the vehicle stalls while driving
the vehicle will not restart after stalling
the vehicle requires holding the key in the on position to drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter motor can cause the vehicle to not start, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle is unable to start
no response from the starter motor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving
the vehicle will not restart after stalling
the vehicle requires holding the key in the on position to drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The small size of the horn button can make it difficult to locate in an emergency situation, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Difficulty locating the horn button in an emergency situation
resulting in accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the main computer can cause various electrical system failures, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Unknown
as the complaint is vague.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front lower ball joint can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, and can also cause the wheel to detach, resulting in a loss of steering control.
symptoms: Squeaking noise coming from the wheel well
feeling as if the wheels are going to fall off
loud pop sound heard while driving
vehicle stalls
and the vehicle pulls to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front suspension can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, and can also cause the wheel to detach, resulting in a loss of steering control.
symptoms: Car pulls to one side
alignment issues
tire wear
and rattling noise in the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: ABS Brake Module and Actuator Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS brake module and actuator can cause a change in braking ability, leading to accidents.
symptoms: ABS light illuminating on the dashboard
slight change in braking ability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine imbalance and vibration can cause the vehicle to vibrate excessively, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle vibrates when foot is on acceleration pedal
rattling noise in the vehicle
and vibrations felt in the steering wheel.
